      <description>&lt;article class=&#34;talk-entry&#34; id=&#34;optimising-spatial-teamwork-under-uncertainty&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://s3.amazonaws.com/pf-user-files-01/u-59356/uploads/2025-01-17/py73w3t/AAAI_Spatial_Teamwork.mp4&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; class=&#34;talk-entry-thumb&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://geverett.co.uk/images/AAAI_Talk.png&#34; alt=&#34;Optimising Spatial Teamwork Under Uncertainty&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;talk-entry-play&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-play&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-entry-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-entry-header&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;talk-entry-venue&#34;&gt;AAAI 2025&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 class=&#34;talk-entry-title&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://s3.amazonaws.com/pf-user-files-01/u-59356/uploads/2025-01-17/py73w3t/AAAI_Spatial_Teamwork.mp4&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Optimising Spatial Teamwork Under Uncertainty&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;p class=&#34;talk-entry-description&#34;&gt;Research on a novel method for assessing agent teamwork based on spatial coordination using Monte Carlo Tree Search and linear programming. Applied to optimising team defensive structures in football.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-entry-actions&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://s3.amazonaws.com/pf-user-files-01/u-59356/uploads/2025-01-17/py73w3t/AAAI_Spatial_Teamwork.mp4&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; class=&#34;pub-btn&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-play&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Watch talk&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;article class=&#34;talk-entry&#34; id=&#34;the-strain-of-success-a-predictive-model-for-injury-mitigation-and-team-success&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K5a7C4b1Cwc&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; class=&#34;talk-entry-thumb&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://img.youtube.com/vi/K5a7C4b1Cwc/0.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;The Strain of Success: A Predictive Model for Injury Mitigation and Team Success&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;talk-entry-play&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-play&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;talk-entry-body&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;talk-entry-header&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;talk-entry-venue&#34;&gt;MIT Sloan 2024&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 class=&#34;talk-entry-title&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K5a7C4b1Cwc&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;The Strain of Success: A Predictive Model for Injury Mitigation and Team Success&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;p class=&#34;talk-entry-description&#34;&gt;Research on the use of machine learning and reinforcement learning-based search methods to optimise team selections over a season to maximise team success while mitigating player injuries.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
